(190, 6, 1, 308, 502, 0, 0, 2, 477, 'Valid for all performances', '2022-06-20', '23:00:00', 1, '1. To complete your booking take a note of your Voucher Access Code below. One code will allow you to book up to two tickets – maximum one code per screening.<br> 2. To help social distancing, we have removed every other seat, so if you are booking 2 tickets, you will only be able to select the seats available which may not be in the same row.<br> 3. Then go <a href=\"https://whatson.bfi.org.uk/\"target=\"_blank\">www.whatsonbfi.org.uk</a>. Enter your code where prompted in the promotional code box top right before you select a film and ticket price – you will not be able to change your ticket price at the end of your booking.<br> 4. Click on the calendar to show you what is screening on Sat 19 and Sun 20. Select your seats. When you are ready, go to the checkout and confirm your booking.<br> 5. Confirmation of your tickets will be sent to your registered email with instructions on where to enter on the day – BFI Southbank is a COVID-secure venue so please allow enough time on the day to check in when you arrive. Full details can be found on the website. If you have any issues please email box.office@bfi.org.uk.<br>', '0.00', '0.00', 3600, 12, 1000, 240, 240, '2001-01-01 00:00:00', 0, 'BFI Southbank ', 'Europe/London', 1, 'Valid throughout National Lottery Cinema Weekend'),
(191, 14469, 1, 216, 300, 0, 0, 2, 285, 'Valid for all performances', '2022-06-20', '23:00:00', 1, '1. Please visit <a href=\"https://www.scottcinemas.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\">www.scottcinemas.co.uk</a> and select the venue<br> 2. Once on the venue homepage, select the film and screening time you would prefer.<br> 3. Select Adult Standard ticket, a seat (subject to availability, standard seating only), then proceed to checkout.<br> 4. Click Redeem a Code and enter the code to redeem the 100% discount on your ticket.<br> 5. You will then receive your tickets via email. We look forward to seeing you!<br>', '0.00', '0.00', 3600, 12, 1000, 240, 240, '2001-01-01 00:00:00', 0, 'Scott Cinemas - Barnstaple', 'Europe/London', 1, 'Valid throughout National Lottery Cinema Weekend'),
